query:
INSERT INTO priceHistory (userId, itemId, purchasePrice, sellingPrice, changedAt)
SELECT 1, id, purchasePrice, sellingPrice, createdAt
FROM items
WHERE itemCode = 'SM-A17568256'
LIMIT 1
